Diamond Platnumz has offered a helping hand to needy Tanzanian people. Diamond will pay three months' house rent for 500 families as a "kind gesture" during these times of corona pandemic. Announcing on Instagram, he said he is aware most people are affected financially and their businesses as well. "Although I am amongst those affected by this pandemic on economy, with the little that God has blessed me with, I have decided to at least offer a helping hand by paying three months' house rent to 500 families as my kind gesture," he said. The 'Jeje' hitmaker said he will announce the procedure of how the 500 families shall receive the house rent. "I believe I should share your troubles and your happiness, too," he said. Edited by T Jalio